INPUT: 

a=int(input('enter your marks in Accounts:'))
b=int(input('enter your marks in Math:'))
c=int(input('enter your marks in Economics:'))
d=int(input('enter your marks in law:'))

x=(a+b+c+d)
print(x)


if (x>350):
    print("Congratulations! You have passed with A grade.")
elif (x>250):
    print("Congratulations! You have passed with B grade.")
elif (x>150):
    print("You have passed with C grade.")
else:
    print("Alas! You have not passed.")
    
    
    
    OUTPUT:
    
enter your marks in Accounts:100
enter your marks in Math:60
enter your marks in Economics:40
enter your marks in law:50
total marks scored out of 400: 250
You have passed with C grade.
